Mill Street Study
Hennepin County is leading a study to determine the feasibility of adding a trail alongside Mill Street to make it safer and more comfortable for pedestrians. An Open House will take place on April 30 from 6-8 pm at St John the Baptist on 680 Mill Street. Additional Info...

Seasonal Maintenance Workers Needed
The City of Excelsior is accepting applications for seasonal maintenance workers for the spring/summer of 2019. Read on...

Zebra Mussel Control Research Project
An informational meeting will be held on April 23 at 6:00 pm at Deephaven City Hall, 20225 Cottagewood Rd to share information on a zebra mussel control project that is planned for St. Albans Bay (treated area) and Robinson Bay (control area) this summer.
